@startuml Collaboration Diagram
!theme plain
title University Timetabling Solver - Communication/Collaboration Diagram

actor User

rectangle "Timetabling System" {
    
    object "SolverRunner" as Runner <<Controller>>
    object "ITC2019Parser" as Parser <<Parser>>
    object "SolveConfig" as Config <<Configuration>>
    object "Instance" as Instance <<Data Model>>
    object "TimetablingSolver" as Solver <<Solver Engine>>
    object "CpModel" as Model <<OR-Tools Model>>
    object "CpSolver" as CPSolver <<OR-Tools Solver>>
    object "LNSOptimizer" as LNS <<LNS Wrapper>>
    object "SolutionValidator" as Validator <<Validator>>
    object "SolutionResult" as Result <<Result Model>>
    object "SolutionVisualizer" as Visualizer <<View>>
    object "DashboardRenderer" as Dashboard <<Web UI>>
}

' User interactions
User --> Runner : 1: execute(argv)
User --> Dashboard : 10: view results

' Runner orchestration
Runner --> Parser : 2: parse_itc2019_xml()
Runner --> Config : 3: create config
Runner --> Instance : 4: pass to solver
Runner --> Solver : 5: solve_instance()
Runner --> Validator : 8: validate_solution()
Runner --> Visualizer : 9: generate_charts()
Runner --> Dashboard : 9.1: render dashboard

' Parser creates Instance
Parser --> Instance : creates

' Solver collaboration
Solver --> Config : reads parameters
Solver --> Instance : uses constraints
Solver --> Model : 6.1: creates & builds
Solver --> CPSolver : 6.2: solves baseline
Solver --> LNS : 6.3: runs LNS (optional)
Solver --> Result : 7: produces

' LNS collaboration
LNS --> CPSolver : re-solves with hints
LNS --> Result : returns improved

' Validator collaboration
Validator --> Result : validates
Validator --> Instance : checks against

' Visualization collaboration
Visualizer --> Result : reads data
Dashboard --> Visualizer : renders charts

' Numbered message flow (explicit)
Runner -[#red]-> Parser : (1) Load XML
Parser -[#red]-> Instance : (2) Create Instance
Runner -[#blue]-> Config : (3) Configure
Runner -[#blue]-> Solver : (4) Start solving
Solver -[#green]-> Model : (5.1) Build constraints
Solver -[#green]-> CPSolver : (5.2) Baseline solve
Solver -[#orange]-> LNS : (5.3) LNS optimize (optional)
Solver -[#purple]-> Result : (6) Extract solution
Runner -[#brown]-> Validator : (7) Validate
Runner -[#gray]-> Visualizer : (8) Visualize
Runner -[#gray]-> Dashboard : (9) Render HTML

note right of Runner
  Controller component
  orchestrates workflow
end note

note right of Solver
  Core CP-SAT solver with
  LNS optimization wrapper
end note

note bottom of Result
  Central data structure
  shared between components
end note

note right of Dashboard
  Web-based dashboard
  for interactive viewing
end note

@enduml
